snippet.title: Animal Force - Launch Trailer | PS VR
snippet.description:
Assemble your squad of superpowered beasts to save the world from a deadly alien invasion.
Unleash your claws, paws, horns and fangs across huge 3D planetary battlefields in totally immersive 360° virtual reality – deploying mighty critters to fight waves of other-worldly enemies before they kidnap defenseless humans.
Follow Animal Force on our socials!
https://www.facebook.com/OasisGamesConsole/ 
https://twitter.com/OAS_Games 
As well as our Official Site:
http://oasgames.com/en/
